channel.title: Hey! Need a new source
channel.description:
Hey! Lately I've been thinking about remaking my server.... Because my source server (Project 16 V6) has glitches and unwanted built-in features and it's hard to remove it... So I was wondering if there was a completely empty source with nothing installed just like Runescape except without any kinda of npc's, object's, and features... Can someone tell me the link to it or like post the download please?
Thanks. :cool:

item.title: Hey! Need a new source
item.dc:creator: @X_F_U_R_Y_X X F U R Y X
item.description:
@X_F_U_R_Y_X wrote:

What’re those? WinterLove sounds… Uhmm, yah… so they fit my description?

no addons, like summoning (Ugh...), specials, and all that junk. Like its completely empty so I can freely install the things I want without having to delete other things...

[quote=“Syrillia, post:5, topic:156252”][quote author=X F U R Y X link=topic=213203.msg1862079#msg1862079 date=1194052312]
So you mean it has like, not addons, like summoning (Ugh…), specials, and all that junk? Like its completely empty so I can freely install the things I want without having to delete other things?
[/quote]

Literally completely empty. I might have some autospawns like cows and chickens. Maybe the odd shop, but nothing that cant be deleted quicktime.[/quote]

Okay, I’ll give it a try, thanks…
